title: Planet Nomads v0.8.2.0
description: Planet Nomads is a singleplayer sci-fi sandbox game of survival on alien planets through block-style building. You are a lone astronaut scientist crash-landing on a strangely captivating planet. Keeping your wit together and securing your basic survival needs that include food, water and building material is the best start towards figuring out a way out of this messy situation.Planet Nomads delivers a unique gaming experience by combining building, survival and exploration together to make you
